snippet.title: biped Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Join Aku and Sila as they embark on a hilariously fun adventure to light up the Earth for all those who travel the galaxy. Biped will first invade your PC on March 27th, then conquers PS4 and Switch in Q2 2020. But regardless of the platform, it will steal your ❤️

To Wishlist on Steam: http://bit.ly/BipedSteamRelease

Follow us on social to find out more: 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/BipedGame
Instagram https://www.instagram.com/bipedgame/
